item.title: CVE-2023-32458|2024-08-02T15:18:37.297Z -- dell -- dell%20emc%20appsync
item.description: Dell AppSync, versions 4.4.0.0 to 4.6.0.0 including Service Pack releases, contains an improper access control vulnerability in Embedded Service Enabler component. A local malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability during installation leading to a privilege escalation.
